GITHUB:

In GitHub:
Settings → Developer settings → OAuth Apps → New OAuth App. GitHub requires an Application name, Homepage URL, and Authorization callback URL

Use values like this:

Application name: OpenShift GitHub Login
Homepage URL:
https://oauth-openshift.apps.venky-ocp.beyondcloud.online
Authorization callback URL:
https://oauth-openshift.apps.venky-ocp.beyondcloud.online/oauth2callback/github


Dont forget to copy the secret.

oc create secret generic github-secret \
  --from-literal=clientSecret=YOUR_GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET \
  -n openshift-config

  vi github-idp.yaml

